<div class='span12'>
<h2>The influence of the background language Mandarin Chinese on the learning of further languages (French/Spanish): Linguistic and educational perspectives (Institutionalisiertes Forschungsprojekt)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h4>Allgemeine Angaben</h4>
<dl class='attribute_listing'>
<dt>Projektbeginn</dt>
