<dt>Projektende</dt>
<dd>Montag, 31. Dezember 2012</dd>
<dt>Status</dt>
<dd>abgeschlossen</dd>
<dt>Weiterführender Link</dt>
<dd><a href="http://www.lima.uni-hamburg.de/index.php/de/forschung/einzelprojekte/220-the-influence-of-the-background-language-mandarin-chinese-on-the-learning-of-further-languages-frenchspanish-linguistic-and-educational-perspectives" target="_blank">http://www.lima.uni-hamburg.de/index.php/de/forschung/einzelprojekte/220-the-influence-of-the-background-language-mandarin-chinese-on-the-learning-of-further-languages-frenchspanish-linguistic-and-educational-perspectives</a></dd>
